C</label>\n<input class=\"wb-srch-q form-control\" id=\"wb-srch-q\" list=\"wb-srch-q-ac\" maxlength=\"170\" name=\"q\" placeholder=\"Search IRCC\" size=\"34\" type=\"search\" value=\"\"/>\n<datalist id=\"wb-srch-q-ac\">\n</datalist>\n</div>\n<div class=\"form-group submit\">\n<button class=\"btn btn-primary btn-small\" id=\"wb-srch-sub\" name=\"wb-srch-sub\" type=\"submit\"><span class=\"glyphicon-search glyphicon\"></span><span class=\"wb-inv\">Search</span></button>\n</div>\n</form>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n<hr/>\n<div class=\"container\"><div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<nav class=\"gcweb-menu\" typeof=\"SiteNavigationElement\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Menu</h2>\n<button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"wb-inv\">Main </span>Menu <span class=\"expicon glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down\"></span></button>\n<ul aria-orientation=\"vertical\" data-ajax-replace=\"/content/dam/canada/sitemenu/sitemenu-v2-en.html\" role=\"menu\">\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/jobs.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Jobs and the workplace</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://travel.gc.ca/\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Travel and tourism</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/business.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Business and industry</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/benefits.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Benefits</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/health.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Health</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/taxes.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Taxes</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/environment.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Environment and natural resources</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/defence.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">National security and defence</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/culture.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Culture, history and sport</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/policing.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Policing, justice and emergencies</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/transport.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Transport and infrastructure</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.international.gc.ca/world-monde/index.aspx?lang=eng\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Canada and the world</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/finance.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Money and finances</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/science.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Science and innovation</a></li>\n<li role=\"presentation\"><a href=\"https://www.canada.ca/en/services/life-events.html\" role=\"menuitem\" tabindex=\"-1\">Manage life events</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<nav id=\"wb-bc\" property=\"breadcrumb\"><h2 class=\"wb-inv\">You are here:</h2><div class=\"container\"><ol class=\"breadcrumb\">\n<li><a href=\"/en.html\">Canada.ca</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/services/immigration-citizenship.html\">Immigration and citizenship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship.html\">Canadian citizenship</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/stateless.html\">Canadian citizenship for stateless people</a></li>\n</ol></div></nav>\n</header>\n</div>\n</div>\n<main class=\"container\" property=\"mainContentOfPage\" resource=\"#wb-main\" typeof=\"WebPageElement\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<!-- 1: GC Subway navigation -->\n<nav class=\"gc-subway provisional\">\n<h1>Apply for Canadian citizenship: Stateless people</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/stateless/who.html\">Who can apply</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/stateless/forms-documents.html\">Get the forms and documents</a>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/stateless/submit.html\">Submit your application</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"active\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/stateless/wait.html\">Wait for a decision</a></li>\n</ul>\n</nav>\n<!-- 2: Title -->\n<h1 class=\"gc-thickline\" id=\"wb-cont\" property=\"name\">Wait for a decision</h1>\n<p>Learn what happens after you submit your application and how you can track its status.</p>\n<h2>On this page</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#first\">What happens first</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#after\">After we process your application</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#check\">Check and update your application</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#quality\">Quality Assurance Program</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"first\">What happens first</h2>\n<p>When the Case Processing Centre in Sydney (CPC Sydney) receives your application, the staff there will check that you</p>\n<ul>\n<li>included all the required documents</li>\n<li>paid the correct fees</li>\n</ul>\n<!--  <div class=\"cnjnctn-type-or cnjnctn-sm wb-eqht\">\n        <section class=\"cnjnctn-col\">\n            <div class=\"well hght-inhrt p-0\">\n            \n                <p class=\"text-center mrgn-tp-0\">If your application is <strong>complete</strong></p>\n                <p class=\"text-center\">We’ll start processing your application and send you an acknowledgement of receipt letter.</p>\n            \n            </div>\n        \n    \n        </section>\n        <section class=\"cnjnctn-col\">\n        \n            <div class=\"well hght-inhrt p-0\">\n            \n                <p class=\"text-center mrgn-tp-0\">If your application is <strong>incomplete</strong> or missing fees</p>\n                <p class=\"text-center\">We’ll return your application to you.</p>\n            \n            </div>\n\n        </section>\n    </div> -->\n<p>If your application is <strong>complete</strong>, we’ll start processing your application and send you an acknowledgement of receipt letter.</p>\n<p>If your application is <strong>incomplete</strong> or missing fees, we’ll return your application to you.</p>\n<p>After the initial review, CPC Sydney sends your application to a local IRCC office to make a final decision. You may be asked to attend an interview with a citizenship officer or a citizenship judge.</p>\n<h2 id=\"after\">After we process your application</h2>\n<div class=\"bg-success p-3 mrgn-tp-lg custom-brdr-rnd\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-2 col-md-1\"> <span class=\"mrgn-tp-0 h2\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-ok-sign text-success\"></span></span> </div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-10 col-md-11\">\n<p class=\"mrgn-tp-0\">If your application is <strong>approved</strong></p>\n<p>You receive your Canadian citizenship certificate by mail.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"bg-danger p-3 mrgn-tp-lg custom-brdr-rnd\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-2 col-md-1\"><span class=\"h2 mrgn-tp-0\"> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-remove-sign text-danger\"></span></span> </div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-10 col-md-11\">\n<p class=\"mrgn-tp-0\">If your application is <strong>not approved</strong></p>\n<p>You receive a letter that explains why your application was refused.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"check\">Check and update your application</h2>\n<p>You can check your application status online <strong>only after</strong> you’ve received an acknowledgement of receipt (AOR) letter or email.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You’ll get an AOR once we’ve received your application and have checked that it’s complete.</li>\n<li>It can take some time for you to receive it.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Learn how to <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/become-canadian-citizen/after-apply-next-steps/status.html\">understand your application status</a>.</p>\n<p>We may contact you to get more information if your case is <a href=\"http://www.ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/answer.asp?qnum=1169&amp;top=5\">non-routine</a>.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/check-status.html\">Check your application status</a></p>\n<section class=\"mfp-hide modal-dialog modal-content overlay-def\" id=\"centred-popup\">\n<header class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title h4\">Change your address</h2>\n</header>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n<p>Tell us right away if you change your address at any time after you submit your application, <strong>even if you arrange for mail forwarding</strong>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Canada Post doesn't forward parcels (An application package is a parcel).</li>\n<li>If we return your application package to you at a forwarding address, you won't get it and it will be sent back to us.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>After</strong> you become a Canadian citizen, you don't need to tell us if you change your address.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/change-address.html\">Learn how to change your address</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<h3>When to contact us</h3>\n<p>Do <strong>not</strong> contact us about your application status if you <strong>haven’t received an acknowledgement of receipt letter</strong>.</p>\n<p>While we are processing your application, contact us if you</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a aria-controls=\"centred-popup\" class=\"wb-lbx\" href=\"#centred-popup\" role=\"button\">change your address</a></li>\n<li>change other contact information, such as your email address or telephone number</li>\n<li>plan to leave Canada for more than 2 weeks in a row</li>\n<li>can’t <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/application/check-status.html\">check your application status</a> online, and the normal processing time for your application has passed</li>\n<li>are charged with a crime</li>\n<li>applied as part of a group but now want to continue the application by yourself</li>\n<li>want to update any other information in your application</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"mrgn-tp-md\">If you don’t update us</p>\n<ul>\n<li>it may take us longer to process your application <strong>or</strong></li>\n<li>we may refuse or abandon (stop processing) your application</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"mrgn-tp-md\">Due to privacy laws, we can’t give information about your application to anyone unless you <a href=\"http://www.ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/answer.asp?qnum=020&amp;top=4\">consent in writing</a>. For example, if you have difficulty communicating in English or French, you need to provide consent for a family member to contact us about your application.</p>\n<p><a class=\"btn btn-default\" href=\"http://www.ircc.canada.ca/english/contacts/web-form.asp\">Contact us</a></p>\n<h3>If you don’t want to become a Canadian citizen anymore</h3>\n<p>Find out <a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/services/canadian-citizenship/become-canadian-citizen/after-apply-next-steps/withdraw.html\">how to withdraw or cancel your application</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwscolumns section\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-8\">\n<div class=\"mwsgeneric-base-html parbase section\">\n<div id=\"quality\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"reference parbase section\"><div class=\"cq-dd-paragraph\"><div class=\"mwsgeneric_base_html mwsgeneric-base-html parbase\">\n<span data-incl-name=\"qa-program-eng\"></span>\n<h2>Quality Assurance Program </h2>\n<p>Our Quality Assurance Program randomly selects applications for a detailed review. If your application is selected, we’ll </p>\n<ul>\n<li>let you know by email or mail</li>\n<li>ask you to provide additional information </li>\n<li>schedule an interview with our official, which will help us to\n        <ul>\n<li>confirm the accuracy of the documents and information you provided </li>\n<li>make sure you filled out your application correctly </li>\n<li>verify that you meet all the citizenship requirements </li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mwsmediaplayer section\">\n<script> \n(function injectCSS() {\n    const css = `\n     .custom-brdr-rnd {\n         border-radius: 20px;\n       }\n\n    `;\n    const style = document.createElement('style');\n    style.textContent = css;\n    document.head.appendChild(style);\n  })();\n\n</script>\n</div>\n<section class=\"pagedetails\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">Page details</h2>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-8 col-md-9 col-lg-9\">\n<div class=\"wb-disable-allow\" data-ajax-replace=\"/etc/designs/canada/wet-boew/assets/feedback/page-feedback-en.html\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<gcds-date-modified>\n\t2025-09-11\n</gcds-date-modified>\n</section>\n</main>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"newpar new section\">\n</div>\n<div class=\"par iparys_inherited\">\n<div class=\"global-footer\">\n<footer id=\"wb-info\">\n<h2 class=\"wb-inv\">About this site</h2>\n<div class=\"gc-contextual\"><div class=\"container\">\n<nav>\n<h3>Immigration and citizenship</h3>\n<ul class=\"list-col-xs-1 list-col-sm-2 list-col-md-3\">\n<li><a href=\"https://ircc.canada.ca/english/helpcentre/results-by-topic.asp?top=5\">Help Centre</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/en/immigration-refugees-citizenship/corporate/contact-ircc.html\">Cont